@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tgrswu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.28 * v1 + 0.11)) + (v2 / wp.sin(tmp + 0.38)))
    v1 = 0.51
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v0 + 0.71 * v1 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
